Hallie Todd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hallie_Todd 0 Hallie Todd (born Hallie Jane Eckstein; January 7, 1962) is an American actress, producer and writer, known for her roles as Penny Waters on Brothers and as Jo McGuire on Lizzie McGuire.
